#: src/widgets/about/ui/About.tsx
msgid "I build platforms that brings calm, simplicity, and reliability, so product teams can move fast, sleep well, and ship with confidence."
msgstr "I build platforms that brings calm, simplicity, and reliability, so product teams can move fast, sleep well, and ship with confidence."

#: src/widgets/about/ui/About.tsx
msgid "I shipped my first production code at 19, but I quickly realized that 'shipping fast' often came at the cost of stability and personal well-being. Living through high-stakes on-call rotations taught me that reliability isn't just a feature... it's the foundation of a sustainable team. I shifted my focus to building safely and prioritizing predictable operations, resulting in systems that support long-term growth."
msgstr "I shipped my first production code at 19, but I quickly realized that 'shipping fast' often came at the cost of stability and personal well-being. Living through high-stakes on-call rotations taught me that reliability isn't just a feature... it's the foundation of a sustainable team. I shifted my focus to building safely and prioritizing predictable operations, resulting in systems that support long-term growth."

